##DATA d:/git/adpoBenchmark/data/sim_0_0_0_0.csv 
##MAP   Aa = AMT CObs = IOBS id = ID time = TIME WT = WT
##MODEL test()  
  { 
  deriv(Aa = - Ka * Aa)
  deriv(A1 = Ka * Aa - Vmax * C / (Km  + C ))

  C = A1 / V
  dosepoint(Aa, idosevar = AaDose, infdosevar = AaInfDose, infratevar =  AaInfRate)
  error(CEps = 0.5) 
  observe(CObs=C + CEps * sqrt(1 + C^2 * (CMultStdev/sigma())^2)) 
  fixef( CMultStdev = c(0,1,))
  stparm(Vmax = tvVmax * exp( nVmax ))
  fixef(tvVmax= c(100, 4000, ))  
  stparm(Km = tvKm )
  fixef(tvKm= c(100, 4000, ))  
  fcovariate(WT)
  stparm(V = tvV  )
  fixef(tvV= c(1, 50, )) 
  stparm(Ka = tvKa )
  fixef(tvKa= c(0.01, 1.2, 3))   




  ranef(diag(nVmax) = c(0.547))

  } 
##ESTARGS
  ODE=DVERK sort=FALSE method=FOCE-ELS stdErr=Auto-Detect numIterations = 10 maxStepsODE = 100000000
